* Toppar stream file generated by
* CHARMM General Force Field (CGenFF) program version 2.5
* For use with CGenFF version 4.6
*

read rtf card append
* Topologies generated by
* CHARMM General Force Field (CGenFF) program version 2.5
*
36 1

! "penalty" is the highest penalty score of the associated parameters.
! Penalties lower than 10 indicate the analogy is fair; penalties between 10
! and 50 mean some basic validation is recommended; penalties higher than
! 50 indicate poor analogy and mandate extensive validation/optimization.

RESI MAIN           0.000 ! param penalty=  56.000 ; charge penalty=   7.031
GROUP            ! CHARGE   CH_PENALTY
ATOM CL1    CLGA1  -0.089 !    4.414
ATOM C1     CG311  -0.061 !    7.031
ATOM CL2    CLGA1  -0.089 !    4.414
ATOM C2     CG301  -0.501 !    7.030
ATOM CL3    CLGA3   0.090 !    3.664
ATOM CL4    CLGA3   0.090 !    3.664
ATOM CL5    CLGA3   0.090 !    3.664
ATOM H      HGA1    0.220 !    1.386
ATOM LP1    LPH     0.050 ! on CL1
ATOM LP2    LPH     0.050 ! on CL2
ATOM LP3    LPH     0.050 ! on CL3
ATOM LP4    LPH     0.050 ! on CL4
ATOM LP5    LPH     0.050 ! on CL5

BOND CL1  C1  
BOND C1   CL2 
BOND C1   C2  
BOND C2   CL3 
BOND C2   CL4 
BOND C2   CL5 
BOND C1   H   

LONEPAIR COLI LP1    CL1    C1     DIST 1.6400 SCAL 0.0
LONEPAIR COLI LP2    CL2    C1     DIST 1.6400 SCAL 0.0
LONEPAIR COLI LP3    CL3    C2     DIST 1.6400 SCAL 0.0
LONEPAIR COLI LP4    CL4    C2     DIST 1.6400 SCAL 0.0
LONEPAIR COLI LP5    CL5    C2     DIST 1.6400 SCAL 0.0

END

read param card flex append
* Parameters generated by analogy by
* CHARMM General Force Field (CGenFF) program version 2.5
*

! Penalties lower than 10 indicate the analogy is fair; penalties between 10
! and 50 mean some basic validation is recommended; penalties higher than
! 50 indicate poor analogy and mandate extensive validation/optimization.

BONDS

ANGLES
CG311  CG301  CLGA3    97.00    111.20 ! MAIN , from CG331 CG301 CLGA3, penalty= 1.5
CG301  CG311  CLGA1    88.00    111.20 ! MAIN , from CG331 CG311 CLGA1, penalty= 2.7

DIHEDRALS
CLGA3  CG301  CG311  CLGA1      0.1000  3     0.00 ! MAIN , from SG311 CG321 CG321 SG311, penalty= 56
CLGA3  CG301  CG311  HGA1       0.2700  3     0.00 ! MAIN , from CLGA3 CG301 CG331 HGA3, penalty= 11

IMPROPERS

END
RETURN
